# ViLoLabs — Cloudflare Pages _redirects
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Rules are evaluated TOP-TO-BOTTOM, first match wins. Status 200 = rewrite
# (URL stays in the bar, target served). Client-side JS reads location.pathname
# and renders the slug-specific view.
#
# ⚠️ HARD-WON RULES OF THIS FILE (each was a production bug):
# 1. Rewrite targets must NOT contain ".html" — Cloudflare silently DROPS the
#    rule (e.g. "/worksheets/index.html" killed the slug catch-all → every
#    shared worksheet URL 404'd). Use the directory form "/worksheets/".
# 2. A splat like /worksheets/* swallows REAL files in that folder too. The
#    worksheet data files (worksheet-seo.js, seo-keywords.json) therefore live
#    in /assets/, NOT /worksheets/. Never put real assets under a splat path.

# Pretty URLs for /worksheets/<slug>  →  serve the landing page
/worksheets/*    /worksheets/    200

# Tool-share pretty URLs — /tools/<tool>/<slug>  →  serve /tools/<tool>.html
# (no real files live under these dirs, so the splat is safe here)
/tools/resize-image/*      /tools/resize-image      200
/tools/qr-generator/*      /tools/qr-generator      200
/tools/image-to-pdf/*      /tools/image-to-pdf      200
/tools/compress-image/*    /tools/compress-image    200
/tools/compress-pdf/*      /tools/compress-pdf      200
/tools/merge-pdf/*         /tools/merge-pdf         200

# (Add more redirects here as the site grows.)
